he way in which professionals engage with clients and the organization of treatments. This book will be relevant to a range of helping professionals such as psychotherapists, psychologists and social workers, both in practice and in training"--cProvided by publisher.  a16 0aAttachment behavior. 0aAdulthoodxPsychological aspects.  aBF 575 A86 D36 2015c1hUAAU-Bi0162035230414  aBF 575 A86 D36 2015wLCc1i0162035230414d4/7/2017e4/7/2017kCHECKEDOUTlON_SHELFmUAAUGn3p$150.00rMsYtBOOKu2/4/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n2014180918bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/306382685